pared  to  over  a  half  a  million  per  year  in  China  and  India.  That
is  a  challenge  for  us.  And  I  think  it  is  worth  celebrating  what  you
are  doing,  because  I  really  do  believe  that  you  are  the  solution  to
this,  our  challenge  of  meeting  the  need  for  people  prepared  for
math and science. And so I am happy to join my colleagues in con-
gratulating you.

