think  about  my  own  children  getting  out  of  the  bus  and  pushing
it.  And  you  know,  she  was  thrilled.  They  were  happy.  Everybody
was  fine.  But  I  don’t  think  people  really  understand  what  some  of
these rural communities are dealing with. How can these students
come  to  school  and  think  about  school  when  they  are  dealing  with
