But  in  Alabama,  we  have  been  looking  at  changing  how  we  teach.
And  a  lot  of  times,  we  are  so  squeezed  into  the  afternoon  to  teach
the math and science, that we don’t take the time, or we don’t have
the  time,  to  lay  out  all  of  the  manipulatives  and  the  things  that
turn children on and help them understand the concepts and really
know  what  they  are  doing.  Instead  of  just  being  able  to  add,  why
